headline.print_headline: Virgin Atlantic Plane With Landing-Gear Fault Lands Safely
headline.main: Virgin Atlantic Plane With Landing-Gear Fault Lands Safely

lead_paragraph: A Virgin Atlantic plane with landing-gear problems safely made a "non-standard" landing on Monday at London's Gatwick Airport,  which for a few hours was forced to delay flights taking off and to divert incoming planes.
